KFC is the greatest. Clean atmosphere, big screen digital television to watch while you wait, and always ready with a humorous act. The food is also served extra fast, but watch out for people who have already ordered online, because they might fly in and still leave ahead of you. Also, over the last 9-10 months, KFC Uptown Chicago has been extremely reliable, and all of it's employees are well deserving of both promotions and a raise. Not to mention it is hilarious to film yourself eating their food and upload it online.
